value.value: Catalysis of the reaction: (+)-camphor + putidaredoxin + O2 = (+)-exo-5-hydroxycamphor + oxidized putidaredoxin + H2O.
Catalysis of the reaction: 1R,4R)-bornane-2,5-dione + FMNH2 + O2 = (1R,4R)-5-oxo-1,2-campholide + FMN + H+ + H2O.
Catalysis of the reaction: octane + reduced rubredoxin + O2 = 1-octanol + oxidized rubredoxin + H2O.
Catalysis of the reaction: biphenyl + NADH + H+ + O2 = (2R,3S)-3-phenylcyclohexa-3,5-diene-1,2-diol + NAD+. This reaction requires Fe2+.
Catalysis of the reaction: 4-methoxybenzoate + AH(2) + O2 = 4-hydroxybenzoate + A + formaldehyde + H2O.
Catalysis of the reaction: A + ethylbenzene + H2O = (S)-1-phenylethanol + AH(2).
Catalysis of the reaction: 2 H+ + O2 + p-cymene + 2 reduced [2Fe-2S]-[ferredoxin] = 4-isopropylbenzyl alcohol + H2O + 2 oxidized [2Fe-2S]-[ferredoxin].
Catalysis of the reaction: 4-cresol + acceptor + H2O = 4-hydroxybenzaldehyde + reduced acceptor.
Catalysis of the reaction: AH2 + chloroethene = A + chloride + ethene + H+.
Catalysis of the reaction: 1,2,3,5-tetrahydroxybenzene + 1,2,3-trihydroxybenzene = 1,3,5-trihydroxybenzene + 1,2,3,5-tetrahydroxybenzene.
Catalysis of the reaction: S-adenosyl-L-methionine + a thiol = S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + a thioether.
Catalysis of the reaction: acetone + ATP + CO2 + 2 H2O = acetoacetate + AMP + 4 H+ + 2 phosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction: benzoyl acetyl-CoA + CoA = acetyl-CoA + benzoyl-CoA.
Catalysis of the reaction: 3-hydroxy-5-oxohexanoyl-CoA + CoASH = 3-hydroxybutyryl-CoA + acetyl-CoA.
Catalysis of the reaction: 3-ketopimeloyl-CoA + CoA = glutaryl-CoA + acetyl-CoA.
Catalysis of the reaction: 6-aminohexanoate + alpha-ketoglutarate = glutamate + 6-oxohexanoate.
Catalysis of the reaction: phenol + X-phosphate = XH + phenylphosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction: acetyl-CoA + propanoate = acetate + propanoyl-CoA.
Catalysis of the reaction: acetyl-CoA + (E)-glutaconate = acetate + glutaconyl-1-CoA.
Catalysis of the reaction: S-formylglutathione + H2O = formate + glutathione + H+.
Catalysis of the reaction: 4-hydroxybenzoyl-CoA + H2O = 4-hydroxybenzoate + CoA + H+.
Catalysis of the reaction: 2'-hydroxybiphenyl-2-sulfinate + H2O = biphenyl-2-ol + sulfite.
Catalysis of the reaction: a primary linear alkyl sulfate ester + H2O = a primary alcohol + H+ + sulfate.

Catalysis of the reaction: limonene-1,2-epoxide + H2O = limonene-1,2-diol. Other substrates include alicyclic and 1-methyl-substituted epoxides, such as 1-methylcyclohexene oxide, indene oxide and cyclohexene oxide.
Catalysis of the reaction: biuret + H2O = urea + CO2 + NH3.
Catalysis of the reaction: epsilon-caprolactam + H2O = H+ + 6-aminohexanoate.
Catalysis of the reaction: cyanurate + H2O = 1-carboxybiuret + H+.
Catalysis of the reaction: ammelide + H2O = cyanuric acid + NH3.
Catalysis of the reaction: 2-chloro-4-hydroxy-6-amino-1,3,5-triazine + OH- = 2,4-dihydroxy-6-amino-1,3,5-triazine + Cl-.
Catalysis of the reaction: ammeline + H2O = ammelide + NH3.
Catalysis of the reaction: deisopropylhydroxyatrazine + H2O = NH3 + 2,4-dihydroxy-6-(N'-ethyl)amino-1,3,5-triazine.
Catalysis of the reaction: 5,10-methenyl-5,6,7,8-tetrahydromethanopterin + H2O = N(5)-formyl-5,6,7,8-tetrahydromethanopterin + H+.
Catalysis of the reaction: H2O + 2 H+ + thiocyanate = carbonyl sulfide + NH4.
Catalysis of the reaction: 3,5-dibromo-4-hydroxybenzonitrile + 2 H2O = 3,5-dibromo-4-hydroxybenzoate + NH4. Involved in the bacterial degradation of the herbicide bromoxynil.
Catalysis of the reaction: R-CN + H2O = R-COOH + NH3.
Catalysis of the reaction: 4-(ethylamino)-2-hydroxy-6-(isopropylamino)-1,3,5-triazine + H2O = N-isopropylammelide + ethylamine.
Catalysis of the reaction: N-isopropylammelide + H2O = cyanuric acid + isopropylamine.
Catalysis of the reaction: (2Z,4E)-2-hydroxy-6-oxohepta-2,4-dienoate + H2O = (2Z)-2-hydroxypenta-2,4-dienoate + acetate + H+.
Catalysis of the reaction: dihydrophloroglucinol + OH- = 3-hydroxy-5-oxohexanoate.
Catalysis of the reaction: (2E,4E)-6-(2-aminophenyl)-2-hydroxy-6-oxohexa-2,4-dienoate + H2O = (2E)-2-hydroxypenta-2,4-dienoate + anthranilate + H+.
Catalysis of the reaction: (2Z,4E)-2-hydroxy-6-oxonona-2,4-dienedioate + H2O = (2Z)-2-hydroxypenta-2,4-dienoate + H+ + succinate.
Catalysis of the reaction: 2,4,6-trioxoheptanoate + H2O = acetylpyruvate + acetate.
Catalysis of the reaction: acetylpyruvate + H2O = acetate + H+ + pyruvate.
Catalysis of the reaction: 2,6-dioxo-6-phenylhexa-3-enoate + H2O = 2-oxopent-4-enoate + benzoate + H+.
Catalysis of the reaction: (2Z,4E)-2-hydroxy-6-oxohexa-2,4-dienoate + H2O = 2-oxopent-4-enoate + formate + H+.
Catalysis of the reaction: (S)-2-haloacid + H2O = (R)-2-hydroxyacid + halide.
Catalysis of the reaction: haloacetate + H2O = glycolate + halide.
Catalysis of the reaction: 1-haloalkane + H2O = a primary alcohol + halide.
Catalysis of the reaction: 4-chlorobenzoyl-CoA + H2O = 4-hydroxybenzoyl-CoA + chloride + H+.
Catalysis of the reaction: atrazine + H2O = chloride + H+ + hydroxyatrazine.
